Template: aktin-notaufnahme/db_local
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Is a PostgreSQL Server running locally?

Template: aktin-notaufnahme/db_host
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: What ist the hostname of your PostgreSQL Server?

Template: aktin-notaufnahme/db_port
Type: string
Default: 5432
Description: On which port does your PostgreSQL Server listen?

Template: aktin-notaufnahme/db_user
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: What ist the user for your PostgreSQL Server?
 The user must have privileges to add users and databases.

Template: aktin-notaufnahme/db_pass
Type: password
Default: localhost
Description: What ist the password for your PostgreSQL Server?

